<div class="container">
  <h1>Create a New Wiki</h1>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-4">
     <p>Guidelines to follow when creating new Wikis:</p>
     <ul>
      <li>Always cite your sources.</li>
      <li>No need to warn readers of spoilers.</li>
      <li>Non-free content must comply with U.S. copyright law.</li>
      <li>Plagiarism will get you banned. No exceptions.</li>
     </ul>
   </div>
   <div class="col-md-8">

    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { wiki: @wiki } %>

   </div>
  </div>
</div>